        <p>A filter can be included in the search feature to let users narrow their search based on concepts that you have inserted into topics. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1">Concepts are simply markers that you add to topics that have some kind of relationship with each other. They are also used for inserting concept links into topics.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
